{"word":"G1550 - ἐκδαπανάω - ekdapanáō - ek-dap-an-ah'-o - Spend","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκδαπανάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekdapanáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-dap-an-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spend</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செலவு பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to exhaust by expending, to spend wholly, use up"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1159 - δαπανάω - dapanáō - dap-an-ah'-o/1159\">G1159</a>; to <i>expend</i> (wholly), that is, (figuratively) <i>exhaust:</i> - spend.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}